34 body.
35 (5) Actions against an owner, lessor or possessor of land, buildings or other real property situ-
36 ated in Oregon that seek to recover for, or to prevent, injury on that property and arising out of
37 conduct that occurs in Oregon.
38 (6) Actions between an employer and an employee who is primarily employed in Oregon that
39 arise out of an injury that occurs in Oregon.
40 (7) Actions for professional malpractice arising from services rendered entirely in Oregon by
